[[File:The_Tree_of_Light.jpg|thumb|right|200px|The Tree of Light]]

The '''Tree of Light''' was a tree held sacred by the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon of Endor]]. It was located on the [[Mountain of Light]]. In their beliefs, a holy light that emanated from the tree kept the village safe from daylight incursions by the [[Night Spirit/Legends|Night Spirit]]. The Ewoks believed that the Tree of Light required [[Light Dust]] in order to retain its power. As a right of passage, young warriors often traveled to the tree to administer the holy substance. Those who complete the task were presented a [[Silver Feather of Bravery|Feather of Light]], and the village celebrated the [[Light Festival]].

